data.description: This exceptional North Valley property, ideally situated just west of the El Pueblo Rail Runner, offers an open floor plan, featuring a spacious living/dining/kitchen area, two generous bedrooms, and an impressive 15x21 master bedroom with a 12x20 master bath and two walk-in closets, all surrounding a central courtyard. Enjoy the comfort of radiant heat and the convenience of a central vacuum system. Recent updates include brand new flooring, and for those with hobbies or workspace needs, there's a 14x18 workshop with an overhead door. With an expansive lot of almost half an acre, this property is a must-see for those looking for a unique North Valley residence.
